would be reduced by $51 million for 2021 and 2020, respectively, including the effect of these changes on other tax attributes, with
state income tax amounts included net of federal tax effect. It is reasonably possible that the total amounts of unrecognized tax benefits
will significantly decrease within 12 months by as much
